The project contract is worth 347,500.00. The project commenced March 21, 2014 and finished April 15, 2014. The project manpower consists of 1 carpenter, 2 Mason ,1 Working Foreman and 5 labor. The labor cost for the project is _____.

Originally, the project is estimated to be completed within 14 days but it took us 21 days to complete due to delays. The delays are caused by the difficulty in bringing in materials to the work area, since materials comes from different places. Steel is fetched from Bel Aldea Subdivision, cement is also fetched from both Bel Aldea and Maravilla, then brought to the work area. 

Recommendation:

Accessible water for the project
truck for trasporting materials